column1: # Supporting Information Table 4. List of all samples used in this study. Samples
# identified to be duplicates in the laboratory are denoted with ‘=’. The ecotype
# of all samples was inferred based on where individuals were located in a
# Bayesian tree based on mtDNA control region sequence data. All samples found to
# have site heteroplasmy in the mtDNA control region are denoted by a haplotype
# name with "hpl". Columns I through AT include microsatellite genotype data for
# the 19 loci analyzed in this study, alleles for each locus are labeled "bin1"
